  6  salary number);

SQL> select count(*) from employees;

  COUNT(*)                                                                      
----------                                                                      
       107                                                                      

SQL> select count(*) from wissen_emp;

  COUNT(*)                                                                      
----------                                                                      
       107                                                                      

SQL> create table wissen_nodata as select * from employees where 2=4;

Table created.

SQL> select count(*) from wissen_nodata;

  COUNT(*)                                                                      
----------                                                                      
         0

SQL> desc user_clusters;
 Name                                                                                                              Null?    Type
